cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper focuses on using deep learning techniques to analyze facial images for personality and emotion traits, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of multi-task learning and adversarial loss function also suggests relevance to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential applications of their work in affective computing, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) sub-category.
